hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui.element.base

Interface GuiEditable<T extends GuiEditable<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the class implementing this interface
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ButtonGuiElement, CheckboxGuiElement, ContinuousSliderGuiElement, DiscreteSliderGuiElement, DropdownGuiElement, RadioButtonGuiElement, TextFieldGuiElement

    public interface GuiEditable<T extends GuiEditable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can be optionally interacted with by viewers. Elements that do not implement this interface are not editable by the viewers. Elements are editable by default.
